org.bremersee.pagebuilder

Interface PageBuilder

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    PageBuilderImpl

    public interface PageBuilder

    A page builder creates a Page form a list of elements.

    There are two ways to create a page:

    • The list of elements that build the page is pre-filtered.
      The list of elements is the result of a SQL query for example.
      Than the page must build with buildPage(Iterable, PageRequest, long) .
    • The list of items that build the page is not filtered and contains all available elements.
      Than the page must build with buildFilteredPage(Collection, PageRequest, Object) .

    Author:
    Christian Bremer
